- Sync config (`sync.enabled`, `sync.auth_method`) is per-repo in `CONSCIOUSNESS/config.json`
- First project: opens browser → sign in → token stored globally → sync enabled
- Subsequent projects: `/apgps` detects existing credentials → enables sync immediately, no browser
- The endpoint is validated against `https://ap.consciousness.london` and `https://api.consciousness.london` — local or non-HTTPS endpoints are rejected at sync time

